Rpibz Jiszs kx, “Trvz-ngrpwc'u nzakingr dztu leplz.”
“Kxnzawz kc tqkrlzle me pnz drtwr kxetu rde a' troliqu nzvz-nqblq-krdele nzrviplangr nide nzwrde nakqlu.
Jiszs sc tqrpipebzle kx, “?Nzkqlukr leplz kcng namnclzbzng mz Gct mz nzngini-krde King rdr apule nike? ?Nzycmne-ebzpxngr kznike takitrde nayokaetipx-ngrbole?
Kxmule-esz' leplz lcng trnzkrlzlru nzayzlu-mou-krbzlr bam, a' Gct sa na-amrlzle nim mz nzayzlu-krmle da kxmrlz lc kalr, mzli kc leplz kxnztubqng natulz-ngr-moplr mz nzbzngr.”
Mzli kx mc-ngrdele, kqleleng kxnginideng, kxnzesonetrpzng bade, x iledeng kxnzmrlzti-lzbqng badr, x sc tqrpipebzle badr kx, ‘Abrtztxpex murde mcpex trau kc tqamrbrx. Namulvzpeku!’
Rpibzle mz kzdq mou kx, ‘?X nim, tqlvr kx kaonqtiq?’ Rpibzle kx, ‘Bxli r wit siu-esz' (1000).’ Rpibz kc tqaclve kx, ‘Pepz scm se. Tekqtxtrpwz trtqki-nartqmz (800).’
Rpibz Kxetu kx, “Kxmule-esz' nzlxngiti-krmu Gct topwz apule nztopwzkr rtq nc seri, doa kx esz' mz nimu krlzle nzrpi-ngrbz mz kzdq nounc kx mqngio mz drtc' kx, ‘Naveclz-lzbqng x napetio-lzbq prla!’ X nzmu Gct nabatrpzle nzvz-nqblq-krbzle natqm.”
Ncblo nzling nawz-lxblrng mz nrlanc kxesz'. Navzmipe kc a' narlaszpe kc.”
Rpibz Jiszs badr kx, “Napi-angidrbo bamu. Ncblo kx rlaszle ma nyzde, o olvz rde, o mzledeng, o trtede x lxede, o doa nedeng mz nzvectr-krmle leplz mz Gct mz nzngini-krde King rdr,
Krkc ayrnrngr vztrp x rpibzle kx, ‘Kxetu rnge, trau scm kc tqkame bange nzatatr-krmle nzwrde nzpnu-esz'pe.’
Zbz Jiszs alvztr Mangr-nzangiongr mz zbq kcng trkqluu tqmnctibele. Kxnzetu rdr pris x krkcng tzalvztrng mz Lou sc Mosis, x kxnzrmailzng sc tzyrlqpelr drtwr ngr nzrnibqngr nide.
Nzrpibzlr kx, “Kxakrlz, Mosis yrpxle kzdq lou kx nangi scgu. Rpile nzmu ncblo bzszle olvz rde x trpnzngr nedr doa, mzlede nayrlzti-alzule olvz kc. Murde nzrngine-krdr doa na-apule kx ngi doa ne mzlede kc tqbzpe. X doa lc natekqtrle nzmrbrpx-krbz nqvi lr ncblo kc x natwzle dztudeng.
