Zbz Setzn dwatitrle nabz Judzs Iskariot, kzdq aposol kcng nzpnu-esz'-nrade-li (12).
Rpibz Pita kx, “Kxetu rnge, oliqtipex nzvz-krgi mz presin x mz nzbzmi-krnge nim!”
