Nzwrde kratq Paelzt rpi-mopwzle kx, “?A' memule? ?Da kxtrka kznike alele? Rblxtxm bange nzrmc-krnge da kx takitrde nzbz-krde! A' napibo mz ncblo nengeng naviplalr nide, x sc tzrlrpe-ngrbzlr nzvz-krde.”
Yrtzmq-ani-ngrdele, murde zbq kc ngi zbq ngr nzoliqngr mz Sabat, x sc tqycpe pipz Sabat.
Kx nzesotrpzlr mz mztea kc tzvzkilr, mrlx kc opxm kx navz-rlrupe.
X zyzlr ngr nzalvztrngr angidr lc pnamilxtile nabz leplz kcng tzmnclzbzng mz zmatq ngr alwx x nzbzngr. A' rblxbz mz zmatq kxtrka lcng nzamz-krdr zyzlr lc.
Mzli lcde kx mc Jon Kxawrkxtr nzvz-krm Jiszs, sc tqrpipemle bagr kx, “Nei Sip ne Gct, dela tqvzm.”
X rpi-kzpzle mz ncblo kcng tzamwang kio kx, “Twzamu kio lcng x vznamu. Bzkq ma nyz Trtenge apusr-ngrnamule me nzamwangr da.”
Mz nibrde, nigr badr Jiszs, sc tqvzpekr mz Judiz Provins. Mnctikr badr kzdung mzli mrlcde mz nzawrkxtrngr leplz.
Murde yrlztipeq ncblo nzlvqn, a' krkc tqmwimiq mzli ka trngiu menalzm. X da angidr la tqpime.”
Mz nourla, mzli kc tqvzobe-ngrbzle mz lrpzki, sc tqrmctipele kxnzawz-nrbalq nedeng. X nzrpibzlr kx, “Mrlxm tryagoxpeu, sc tqmnc-nrwxpengr.”
Ninge nou nzlungr, da kc tqwai Trtenge nzngini-krde nou nzlungr.
