Nzmu kx tqsuti drtwrm nzamatqngr nim, bzkq ale-kapqq rkx kcng tqaleq, a' aelwapxngr mzlilxlr, murde nakrlzti lr nrlc amrlx.”
Rpile kx sa nartangrtiku, a' trpnzngr nzmc-krgu nide. X trpnzngr nzkrlz-krbzku mrkc namnc-ngrde. ?Nike tqkxmu nzycmne-krde ke?”
Rpi-mopwz Jiszs kx, “Kxmule-esz' ycmnetr-ngrne ninge esz'-krnge, a' da lcng tqpixng da angidr. Murde, krlzx mrkc tqvzkimc x mrkc navzkix. A' trkrlzwamuu mrkc tqvzkimc x mrkc navzkix.
